Located near the Northern Beaches Hospital in Forest Central Business Park, the available suite is located on level 2 in Building 7. 

The office is located towards the rear of the estate with traffic light controlled egress from both Warringah Rd and Wakehurst Parkway.

Join medical occupiers, such as Cancer Clinics, Dentists, Eye Specialists, PRP Diagnostics, Sonic healthcare, Peninsula Respiratory Group and Sydney Ear Nose and Throat.

+ Fitted out suite with three glazed perimeter offices and open plan areas
+ Cabling and fibre internet installed
+ Great natural light
+ One of the few suites with own kitchenette
+ Lease or Buy, all reasonable offer considered
+ Priced to be sold or leased
+ Window of opportunity to purchase as a going concern, current lease expires 31 March 2020.

For further details please contact exclusive agent CBRE, Ben Byford or Tristan Winterschladen

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LIGHT FILLED, TOP FLOOR FITTED OFFICE – OWN KITCHEN

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:

There is not only basement and on grade parking but an abundance of all day parking within 20m of the complex so all staff can drive to work.

Fully fitted out with absolutely everything incoming tenants can basically plug in and start working. Details of the offering include:

* Exclusive whole top floor of 800sqm
* Presentable open plan reception
* Cabled & partitioned offices
* Boardroom with presentation facilities
* Breakout room & multiple meeting rooms
* Building signage available
* 15 Car spaces included in gross rental
* Ready to inspect - Available April 2009

Why pay high office rents and have the added hassle of worrying about a commercial fit out when it's all included and fully functional?

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Fully fitted out - Exclusive top floor corporate office opportunity

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present Building 10, Frenchs Forest Business Park, Frenchs Forest. This modern three storey commercial freehold building was completed in 2003, with a building area of 1,545sqm*. The property is 100% leased to multinational watch manufacturer - Citizen Australia. Building 10, Frenchs Forest Business Park, Frenchs Forest holds a prime location just moments from the new Northern Beaches Hospital which opened to the public at the end of 2018.

Building 10,  Frenchs Forest Business Park, Frenchs Forest capitalises on the following key attributes:

- 100% leased to multinational watch manufacturer – Citizen Australia. Having operated from the building since its completion in 2003, Citizen Australia is a long-term tenant with international acclaim.   
- Building area of 1,545sqm* plus 29 car spaces 
- Net income of $572,073 per annum*
- Strategic location set for growth for the next 20 years driven by the new hospital and future Frenchs Forest Town Centre
- Significant rental reversion opportunity 


Building 10,  Frenchs Forest Business Park, Frenchs Forest  will be sold via expressions of interest closing on Wednesday, 28 August 2019 at 4.00pm.



For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approximate

Note: All financial figures have been provided by the Vendor. Purchasers are advised to conduct their own independent due diligence.
